-- ============================================================================
-- ARCTOS Seed: EU Cyber Resilience Act (Regulation (EU) 2024/2847)
-- Source: Regulation (EU) 2024/2847 — text adopted 2024-11-23
--
-- Structure: Annex I sets out essential cybersecurity requirements for
-- products with digital elements. Annex II covers vulnerability handling.
-- Annex III lists important products (Class I + II) under stricter regime.
--
-- Compliance becomes applicable in stages from 2026; full applicability 2027.
-- Target modules: isms (product-side IS), ics (controls), tprm (component supply chain)
-- ============================================================================

